{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6117f19fb","title":"再次请辞“总书记”职务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"50a013678c","index":0,"year":1926,"month":7,"day":22,"articleId":"f6117f19fb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"627e1ce86c","type":"paragraph","text":"再次请辞“总书记”职务","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"353de1e8e1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1926年7月22日）","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"15b8677faa","type":"paragraph","text":"在联共（布）中央委员会和","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"5ed99dbb73","type":"paragraph","text":"中央监察委员会联席全会上的讲话","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"fdd7e79857","type":"paragraph","text":"请允许我就宣读的这封信谈几点意见。从这封信中能得出什么样的结论呢？第一个结论是：想办法把斯大林从总书记的职位上调开，由另一个具有同样品质、但不粗暴的人取而代之。出席第十三次代表大会的各代表团都讨论了这个问题。我可以告诉大家一—我不认为这是不谦虚一一所有代表团，无一例外，都主张斯大林留任总书记之职。我手头就有这些决议，如果你们愿意，我可以宣读。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"9fc0e47e99","type":"paragraph","text":"（有人喊道：不需要。）","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"fc263537aa","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然如此，在十三大以后紧接着召开的我党中央一中全会上，我仍然提出辞职。全会对我的辞职请求未予考虑，我记得，还一致决定要我留任总书记。这样一来，我该怎么办呢，同志们？我是身不由已呀，我服从全会的决定。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"c5b1d521fb","type":"paragraph","text":"第二个结论是：由于我是按照党的意志留在总书记岗位上的，我也必须采取一切措施克服粗暴作风，改掉它。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"f9b64ab8d9","type":"paragraph","text":"（有人喊道：还有不谦恭这一条。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"3d502b1c97","type":"paragraph","text":"还有不谦基·...·原载俄罗斯《祖国》杂志","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"f29d2fb5d7","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"75a4f0e1d7","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷一第167页1994年第7期","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"},{"id":"17f18056bb","type":"paragraph","text":"1）指列宁给第十二次代表大会代表的信。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb"}],"page":{"id":"270954bd04","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f6117f19fb","start":2500,"end":2500}}}},"__N_SSG":true}